mutation ($payload:AdminCreateLangInput!)
{
	adminCreateLang (payload:$payload)

		id
		name
		image
		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf
		dir
		sort
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

		dir
		sort
		isActive

		updatedAt
	}
}
